  "text": "In this paper, our goal is to develop robust replica placement techniques for systems that are fraught with uncertainties of when and how many CDN servers fail. To derive a deterministic robustness metric for the static CDN replica placement problem formulation, we make use of the four-step FePIA (Features, Perturbations, Impact, Analysis) procedure [CITATION_1] .",
